<rss version="2.0" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/" xmlns:media="http://search.yahoo.com/mrss/" xmlns:ss="http://contenthub.aol.com/slideshow/"><channel><title><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></title><link/> https://www.engadget.com/ <description><![CDATA[Engadget is a web magazine with obsessive daily coverage of everything new in gadgets and consumer electronics]]></description><language> en-US</language><copyright>版权所有雅虎 2023</copyright><pubDate> Fri, 08 Dec 2023 02:01:53 +0000</pubDate><generator>雅虎 http://yahoo.com </generator><item><title><![CDATA[Supermassive's Dead by Daylight spin-off is 'The Casting of Frank Stone']]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Supermassive Games 刚刚发布了其即将推出的以<em>黎明杀机</em>宇宙为背景的单人互动故事游戏的预告片。 <em>《弗兰克·斯通选角》</em>是一款由角色驱动的叙事冒险游戏，其特点是 Supermassive 开发的游戏<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-quarry-game-release-date-201557551.html">《<em>直到黎明》</em>和<em>《采石场》中的所有角色选择和张力。</em></a></p><p>开发商承诺“强大的生死选择”和全新的角色阵容。 Supermassive 表示，这是“恐怖迷<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://twitter.com/DeadbyDaylight/status/1732460041758822411">体验该系列的全新方式”，</a>这是一种轻描淡写的说法。 <em>《Dead by Deadlight》</em>是一款非对称多人游戏，其中一名玩家是杀手，其他玩家则努力生存。这就像一个非常激烈的捉迷藏版本。显然，单人冒险必须完全不同，预告片肯定倾向于这一点。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="ed839e7744254e0c9faa2c03cdbe6a22"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/E2KAlBy0wqs?si=19XWq6SMG0Kh4_1n" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>正如你所看到的，游戏看起来缓慢、喜怒无常、电影般，这与源材料截然不同。预告片缺乏实际的游戏细节，但有一些树林中手电筒的第一人称镜头，所以这就是问题。</p><p>我们已经<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/until-dawn-developer-supermassive-is-making-a-dead-by-daylight-spin-off-184513565.html">知道这款跨界游戏正在制作中，</a>但在游戏奖上首次亮相的预告片是我们第一次真正看到这款游戏。 《Supermassive》以 B 级恐怖片而闻名，因此<em>《弗兰克·斯通选角》</em>将于 2024 年通过 Steam 和 Windows 推出 Xbox X/S 和 PC 版，这应该是一个好时机。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/supermassives-dead-by-daylight-spin-off-is-the-casting-of-frank-stone-020153336.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/supermassives-dead-by-daylight-spin-off-is-the-casting-of-frank-stone-020153336.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 537f7eb8-fc3d-4385-985c-cbff23e4f9e3</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 02:01:53 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1702001347</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T02:09:10+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="784" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fc45cd990-956c-11ee-bf78-0f389364d128&amp;resize=1400%2C784&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=0f4619718f6ec8646d4b08a4253d1729b3919786" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="784" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fc45cd990-956c-11ee-bf78-0f389364d128&amp;resize=1400%2C784&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=bf082a438ed49f6449c6771d855296eeea60d2a5" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Supermassive Games]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An image of a knight as an ad for the game.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[The Casting of Frank Stone]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[No Rest for the Wicked is a medieval action RPG from the Ori team]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <em>《恶人不息》</em>是 Moon Studios 的新项目，Moon Studios<em>是《奥日与黑暗森林》</em>及其续集的制作团队，它的外观正如你所期望的那样美丽。这是一款自上而下的动作角色扮演游戏，背景设定在 841 年，一个刚刚失去国王的王国。他傲慢而缺乏经验的儿子接管了政权，瘟疫席卷了这片土地。这场骚乱导致一位强大的宗教领袖扩大了她在该地区的影响力，而边缘团体正在尽可能地争夺控制权。你扮演一位名叫 Cerim 的神圣战士，充满魔法并注定要对抗瘟疫。</p><p> <em>《No Rest for the Wicked》</em>强调华丽的中世纪背景中的动作和精确性，并且包括最多可供四名玩家参与的在线合作模式。它将于 2024 年第一季度在 Steam 上抢先体验，最终将登陆 PlayStation 5 和 Xbox Series X/S。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="28835e40e20749ddac96bd113ec6cae6"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HXWom_2Dots?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p> Moon Studios 在游戏奖上以电影预告片首次展示了该项目，并在 3 月 1 日名为“Wicked Inside”的数字展示会上<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://store.privatedivision.com/game/no-rest-for-the-wicked#game-details">承诺提供更多细节</a>。Private Division 正在发行该游戏。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/no-rest-for-the-wicked-is-a-medieval-action-rpg-from-the-ori-team-020119459.html?src =rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/no-rest-for-the-wicked-is-a-medieval-action-rpg-from-the-ori-team-020119459.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 42afe730-00b3-485d-b0f6-18103de6b50d</guid><dc:creator>杰西卡·康迪特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 02:01:19 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1702001592</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T02:13:19+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jessica Conditt]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F1388a440-956d-11ee-bffb-1f3781fef4bd&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=0888a194cf2135459b2b4eae168938724aa0829e" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F1388a440-956d-11ee-bffb-1f3781fef4bd&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=320623542a3cd6b763badcf350a2f0a003cde267" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Moon Studios]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[No Rest for the Wicked]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[No Rest for the Wicked]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[God of War Ragnarok is getting a free roguelite expansion next week]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/god-of-war-ragnarok-review-ps5-162534113.html"><em>《战神诸神黄昏》</em></a>是一款如此庞大的游戏，几乎里面隐藏着整个第二款游戏。然而，对于奎托斯来说，这似乎仍然不够充分。在<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/the-game-awards/">游戏颁奖典礼</a>期间，索尼公布了<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/god-of-war-ragnarok-fastest-selling-sony-exclusive-191147076.html">2022 年热门游戏的</a>以瓦尔哈拉为中心的扩展包。</p><p>不仅如此，它还是免费的。该游戏将于下周（即 12 月 12 日）登陆 PS4 和 PS5 版本的基础游戏。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>就像即将推出的<em>《最后生还者 第二部：重制版》</em>中的<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/the-last-of-us-part-2-remastereds-no-return-trailer-reveals-all-the-playable-characters-160325747.html">不归路模式</a>一样，索尼在这里倾向于 Roguelite 格式。在预告片中，奎托斯被一只飞龙撞到了地上。然后他醒来，听到密米尔告诉他“刚刚发生的事情并不可耻。这都是过程的一部分。我们再出发吧！”</p><p>根据<a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://blog.playstation.com/2023/12/07/god-of-war-ragnarok-valhalla-dlc-revealed-coming-december-12/">PlayStation 博客的说法</a>，在每次运行中，你都必须应对新的敌人组合和一些惊喜。你消灭的敌人越多，你获得的用于永久升级的资源就越多。虽然你可以从主游戏中访问奎托斯的技能树，但每次运行时你都需要坚持使用一个盾牌和一个斯巴达狂暴路径。随着每次尝试的进展，您还将解锁临时福利。</p><p>如果这一切看起来令人畏惧，也不要太担心。有五种难度设置可供选择，并且仍然有大量的<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/god-of-war-ragnarok-accessibility-settings-ps4-ps5-142914661.html">辅助选项</a>可供您使用。</p><p> DLC 似乎还将深入探讨奎托斯故事的新部分。预告片的 YouTube 描述中写道：“与奎托斯一起前往瓦尔哈拉，踏上一段深刻的个人反思之旅，走向他从未想过的未来。”这表明资料片将进入该系列的下一场比赛。虽然你可以随时进入<em>瓦尔哈拉</em>，但开发者建议先完成基础游戏的主要故事。这是因为 DLC 充当了尾声。</p><p>一段时间以来，一直有传言称圣莫尼卡工作室正在为<em>《战神诸神黄昏》开发 DLC。</em>它将免费提供（而且很快！），这对粉丝来说是一个不错的节日小享受。 </p><div id="7e88163ab6ca4e5f9586e382ad99e887"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/C44_HrseDSs?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-getting-a-free-roguelite-expansion-next-week-015012803.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/god-of-war-ragnarok-is-getting-a-free-roguelite-expansion-next-week-015012803.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 0037bb0d-d513-45fc-a152-ee762ba63e68</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 01:50:12 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1702001358</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T02:09:27+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="740" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F7ca7ae60-956a-11ee-b7cf-8648ed68d607&amp;resize=1400%2C740&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=9170eabd008c7ac7e346fba23a305c9c8df26fb5" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="740" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F7ca7ae60-956a-11ee-b7cf-8648ed68d607&amp;resize=1400%2C740&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b6f3b2c0e73485d77df4e9dc4db0a33ce981cf2f" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Santa Monica Studio/PlayStation Studios]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[God of War Ragnarok Valhalla]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[God of War Ragnarok Valhalla]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Big Walk is the next project from the Untitled Goose Game team]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>继 2019 年热门独立<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/untitled-goose-game-multiplayer-update-september-172938841.html"><em>游戏《Untitled Goose Game》</em></a>获得成功后，House House 并不满足于现状，周四晚在 2023 年游戏奖颁奖典礼上公布了其新冒险游戏的首个预告片。 </p><div id="4016f0cb57d4433aa7f27c6031267525"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/vyQPc1i4Rpo?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p> <em>Big Walk</em>看起来在语气和范围上都与其前身有很大不同。该团队将其描述为“一个合作的在线步行者谈话者”，鼓励玩家“在广阔的世界中与亲密的朋友一起闲逛并迷失方向”。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>这款在线合作游戏的背景是一座布满灌木的广阔岛屿，岛上充满了需要揭开的谜团和需要克服的挑战。在预告片中，我们可以看到一群四肢奇特的化身在山坡上漫步，解决谜题，探索奇怪的洞穴，并引爆信号弹。合作将是游戏的重要组成部分。玩家需要共同努力穿越地形并在外出时保持彼此联系。</p><p> “我们在玩在线合作游戏时最喜欢的部分是，它们为你提供了足够的指导，让团队保持良好的势头，但又足够轻松，你基本上可以享受与朋友共度时光。我们希望<em>《Big Walk》</em>能够为玩家提供方向和空间，让他们能够专注于并享受团队动态，无论您是与一个朋友一起玩还是作为一个大团队玩，”House House 的开发者杰克·斯特拉瑟 (Jake Strasser) 在周四的新闻稿中表示。 Big Walk 预计于 2025 年登陆 Steam 和 Epic Game Store。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/big-walk-is-the-next-project-from-the-untitled-goose-game-team-014503842.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/big-walk-is-the-next-project-from-the-untitled-goose-game-team-014503842.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> d89ee307-0536-429a-b49c-5d6420e7c2a4</guid><dc:creator>安德鲁·塔兰托拉</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 01:45:03 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1702000229</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T01:50:32+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Sports & Recreation]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Andrew Tarantola]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fa732f270-956a-11ee-8ffd-be84f362a4fb&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=dc78700b47546eaf707c3c2a9648980bc3658504" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fa732f270-956a-11ee-8ffd-be84f362a4fb&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=37aa85fea343cde78afde5a1cd2306926742ad48" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[House House]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[a bunch of limbed snow men looking things running around outside]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Big Walk by house house]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Windblown is the next game from the creators of Dead Cells]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2019-04-03-dead-cells-story-lore-interview-gdc-2019.html"><em>《死亡细胞》</em></a>开发商 Motion Twin 发布了<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/watch-the-game-awards-2023-here-at-730pm-et-190011911.html">2023 年游戏奖</a>第一批令人瞠目结舌的预告片（在预展中也同样如此）。 <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://windblown.game" data-original-link="https://windblown.game"><em>《Windblown》</em></a>被宣传为“一款快如闪电的动作类 Rogue 游戏”，“将动作类 Rogue 类型的速度提升到了一个全新的水平”。</p><p> <em>《风吹》的故事</em>发生在方舟，一个空中村庄，充满了“无辜的灵魂”。它带着哨兵大军绕着致命的漩涡运行，威胁要“吞噬”主角的空中家园。在单人或多人游戏中，你将控制名为“跳跃者”的角色，他们“吸收前人阵亡战士的记忆，学习如何掌握前辈的战斗风格，以释放他们的全部潜力。” </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="bfc87b18ed7645cd81ef33613633ee17"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/shPyfu6aP58?si=H5WJAv8uVgkvYQHQ" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen></iframe></div><p>游戏的宣传语邀请你在快节奏的战斗中“找到自己的节奏”，预告片似乎也证实了这一点。它的过场动画和游戏玩法都采用了卡通渲染的艺术风格，当你连续死了 20 次时，至少应该给你带来足够的视觉享受。</p><p> <em>《Windblown》</em>计划于 2024 年在 PC 上抢先体验。您现在就可以将其添加到您的<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1911610/Windblown/" data-original-link="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1911610/Windblown/">Steam 愿望清单</a>中。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/windblown-is-the-next-game-from-the-creators-of-dead-cells-012941545.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/windblown-is-the-next-game-from-the-creators-of-dead-cells-012941545.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 7ee406fe-f4cb-4822-a04b-799010f57e6b</guid><dc:creator>威尔·尚克林</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 01:29:41 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701998981</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T01:29:46+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Will Shanklin]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F9ddf5260-9568-11ee-b3cd-90fe55f1b0aa&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=e485cbb75bf2f6070a216d4d48f2a69b0437530c" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F9ddf5260-9568-11ee-b3cd-90fe55f1b0aa&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ffe1b7d734daa13abaa7010159f0db2b2ad44682" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Motion Twin]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Still from the trailer for Windblown, a visually striking roguelike game. A player-controller character leaps high with a sword to take on a fierce enemy on a floating island.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Windblown]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Here's a new trailer for that cool-looking fantasy RPG from the Persona 5 team]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Atlus 及其子公司 Studio Zero 终于在游戏奖上发布了即将推出的 RPG <em>Metaphor: ReFantazio</em>的<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=waztPdM5Yfo"><ins>新预告片</ins></a><em>。</em>该游戏由<em>《女神异闻录 5》背后的许多才华横溢的人执导，</em>包括导演桥野桂和<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/spotify-persona-5-4-3-fes-2-pq-dancing-arena-soundtracks-104349652.html"><ins>作曲家目黑正司。</ins></a>主要区别是什么？这款游戏发生在一个奇幻的环境中，看不到高中或会说话的猫。 </p><div id="93aa20bb9b2e4e97aa128a0abdb556b0"><iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/waztPdM5Yfo?si=UlZJzNORYjwaurIk" title="YouTube 视频播放器" frameborder="0" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div><p>这款游戏<a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/metaphor-refantazio-is-a-fantasy-rpg-from-the-team-behind-persona-5-183345120.html"><ins>最初是在今年早些时候被预告的，</ins></a>但我们所拥有的只是一个标题和一个小的公告预告片。现在这个预告片是真实的，有完整的配音、动画和大量的实际游戏玩法。带有实际游戏玩法的视频游戏预告片，多么新颖的概念。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>至于游戏玩法，战斗看起来与《女神异闻录》类似，尽管没有使用名义上的野兽。该游戏由各种各样的角色组成，如果你盯着菜单，你可以看到一些强大的社交元素的迹象，这与《女神异闻录》系列的另一个相似之处。</p><p>还有一种蒸汽朋克的氛围贯穿始终，这对于电子游戏来说总是一个不错的选择。谁知道呢，也许世界上某个地方有一扇险恶的蓝色门，里面住着一个令人毛骨悚然的老人。<em>隐喻：ReFantazio — 《皇家锦标赛》，</em>史克威尔艾尼克斯喜欢的名字，将于明年秋季在 Xbox X/S 和 PC 上推出。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/heres-a-new-trailer-for-that-c​​ool-looking-fantasy-rpg-from-the-persona-5-team-012127188.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/heres-a-new-trailer-for-that-cool-looking-fantasy-rpg-from-the-persona-5-team-012127188.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 36e02c5d-8e52-4f6c-9f02-bb369f1a1dde</guid><dc:creator>劳伦斯·邦克</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 01:21:27 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701998488</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T01:21:33+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Video Games]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Lawrence Bonk]]></category><media:content height="786" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fd8cd7e20-9567-11ee-bf7d-bb02be499f13&amp;resize=1400%2C786&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=e7a096217a5fd2127f9f88474dc2f9a6c55f751d" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="786" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fd8cd7e20-9567-11ee-bf7d-bb02be499f13&amp;resize=1400%2C786&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=99905c8026d34b869aadf8fa26ba91d8bf0af8d7" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Atlus]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[An ad for the game on a paper background.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Metaphor: ReFantazio]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Exodus is a new sci-fi RPG from former BioWare, 343 and Naughty Dog developers]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <em>《Exodus》</em>是<a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.archetype-entertainment.com/">Archetype Entertainment</a>的第一款游戏，Archetype Entertainment 是 Wizards of the Coast 于 2019 年成立的工作室，其员工都是来自 BioWare、343 Industries、Naughty Dog 和其他 AAA 机构的前开发人员。 <em>《Exodus》</em>是一款宏大而大胆的科幻角色扮演游戏，涉及时间膨胀，即时间过得比我们在高速旅行中习惯的要慢，导致星际探险家比他们家乡的朋友和家人活得更久。</p><p>在<em>《出埃及记》</em>中，人类被迫放弃地球，在充满敌意的星系中建立新的文明。玩家扮演旅行者，负责探索遥远的太阳系以获取先进的外星技术。旅行者以几天为单位计算的事情，其他人类所经历的却是几十年。有了这种想法，玩家的选择将导致蝴蝶效应在人类的新星球上产生涟漪，特别是在他们自己所爱之人的生活中，而旅行者将见证这些效应在几代人的时间里上演。 </p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><div id="f1db3aeb85214308bd2b493f948c172d"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/jsCvugLI61I?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div><p>玩家的选择是<em>《出埃及记》</em>的重要组成部分，影响着个人的战斗时刻并有助于塑造整个故事情节。该游戏包括外星武器和经典枪战、深入的进程系统和大量同伴角色（是的，浪漫已经摆在桌面上）。此外，马修·麦康纳以某种方式参与了<em>《出埃及记》</em> ，他在<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/watch-the-game-awards-2023-here-at-730pm-et-190011911.html">游戏奖</a>上展示了这款游戏，并发布了首个预告片。</p><p> Archetype 是威世智的一个部门，拥有众多出色的科幻电子游戏人才。其中包括工作室负责人 James Ohlen（ <em>《博德之门</em>》、 <em>《龙腾世纪：起源</em>》）、执行制片人 Chad Robertson（ <em>《星球大战：旧共和国</em>》）、导演 Chris King（ <em>《光环 4</em> 》）和叙事导演 Drew Karpyshyn（《<em>质量效应》</em> 、 <em>《质量效应 2</em> 》） 。 <em>《出埃及记》</em>中对时间膨胀和个人损失的关注凸显了团队想要打造一款情感、叙事驱动的游戏的愿望，其中动作是一个引人入胜但又是补充的功能——而且他们有足够的简历来实现这一目标。</p><p> <em>《Exodus》</em>正在针对 PlayStation 5、Xbox Series X/S 和 PC 进行开发。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/exodus-is-a-new-sci-fi-rpg-from-former-bioware-343-and-naughty-dog-developers-011433508.html ?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/exodus-is-a-new-sci-fi-rpg-from-former-bioware-343-and-naughty-dog-developers-011433508.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 820d386d-a4bd-46b8-9404-a9d4a95b9968</guid><dc:creator>杰西卡·康迪特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 01:14:33 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701998675</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T01:24:40+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Arts & Entertainment]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Jessica Conditt]]></category><media:content height="785" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F28aa51b0-955a-11ee-b3ee-fbea67ca941b&amp;resize=1400%2C785&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=da84e2ee25757699b9bf767bd7aa4ac536db3ff2" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="785" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F28aa51b0-955a-11ee-b3ee-fbea67ca941b&amp;resize=1400%2C785&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=8d7e821531ab9b7c71dc99a00830e9d9f714d69b" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Archetype Entertainment]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Exodus]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Exodus]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Thrasher looks like another nightmare-inducing game from the artist behind Thumper]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p><a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/tag/the-game-awards/">游戏奖</a>在预展期间发布了一系列引人入胜的公告，取得了良好的开端。 <em>Thrasher</em>是即将推出的最新游戏之一，它出自 2016 年噩梦工厂<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/thumper-pocket-edition-apple-arcade-133019149.html"><em>Thumper</em></a>背后的艺术家和作曲家之手。</p><p> <em>Thrasher</em>会看到你在黎明时分控制一条太空鳗鱼。你需要掌握“快节奏的手势控制”才能将这种生物进化成所谓的巨型野兽。虽然它可能不是<em>Thumper</em>的直接续集，但预告片表明它将分享前作的一些 DNA。似乎又会出现令人心碎的视觉效果，与脉动、焦虑的配乐相匹配。我已经很害怕了</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p><em>Thrasher</em>将于 2024 年登陆 PC、游戏机和虚拟现实平台。 </p><div id="73d8d987634c4e8fa1bb5ba03e40c252"><div style="left:0;width:100%;height:0;position:relative;padding-bottom:56.25%;"><iframe src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/d2EqoXAEwFg?rel=0" style="top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;position:absolute;border:0;" allowfullscreen="" scrolling="no" data-embed-domain="www.youtube.com"></iframe></div></div><p></p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/thrasher-looks-like-another-nightmare-inducing-game-from-the-artist-behind-thumper-010802152.html?src=rss]] >; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/thrasher-looks-like-another-nightmare-inducing-game-from-the-artist-behind-thumper-010802152.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> c5c9e225-f026-4214-ac66-d749a480ef18</guid><dc:creator>克里斯·霍尔特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 08 Dec 2023 01:08:02 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701997683</ingested><modified> 2023-12-08T01:08:05+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Consumer Discretionary]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Kris Holt]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F8d817090-9565-11ee-a96f-11a60823ecad&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=f30f4835eb43d3f981843563c62b7b0328682d94" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2F8d817090-9565-11ee-a96f-11a60823ecad&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=965d7d85bd1a46df1f4d35613783bd4fcd6cbd85" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Puddle / Creature]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Thrasher]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Thrasher]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Intuit is shutting down Mint, its popular free budget-tracking app]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> <a data-i13n="cpos:1;pos:1" href="https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-11-01/intuit-winds-down-personal-finance-app-mint-shifts-users-to-credit-karma?sref=10lNAhZ9#xj4y7vzkg"><em>据彭博社</em></a>报道，Intuit 正在关闭其免费预算应用程序 Mint，该应用程序在 2021 年拥有 360 万活跃用户。当 Mint 消失后，该公司将把用户吸收到其名为 Credit Karma 的另一项服务中。 Intuit 发言人告诉 Engadget，Mint 将在 2024 年 3 月 24 日之前上市。</p><p> Mint 在其产品中写道：“Credit Karma 很高兴邀请所有 Minters 在 Credit Karma 上继续他们的金融之<a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://mint.intuit.com/blog/mint-app-news/intuit-credit-karma-welcomes-minters/">旅</a>，他们将可以使用 Credit Karma 的一系列功能、产品、工具和服务，包括 Mint 的一些最受欢迎的功能。” <a data-i13n="cpos:2;pos:1" href="https://mint.intuit.com/blog/mint-app-news/intuit-credit-karma-welcomes-minters/">博客</a>。该公司指出，Mint 的产品团队和一些功能已经转移给 Credit Karma。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p> Mint 帮助用户管理预算、跟踪费用并跟踪订阅和每月账单，这样您就无需支付滞纳金。 Intuit 于 2009 年以 1.7 亿美元收购了该公司，Mint <a data-i13n="cpos:3;pos:1" href="https://mint.intuit.com/blog/updates/why-mint-com-plus-intuit-is-a-big-idea/">表示此次收购</a>将有助于将该应用程序带给更多数百万用户。</p><p> Intuit 将把用户转移到 Credit Karma（它<a data-i13n="cpos:4;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/2020-02-24-intuit-buys-credit-karma-for-7-1-billion.html">于 2020 年收购的</a>一家公司），尽管它们并不完全相同。 Credit Karma 更像是一款银行应用程序，可让用户查看交易、监控信用并查看多个账户，但缺乏 Mint 对许多人有吸引力的预算跟踪功能。 Intuit <a data-i13n="cpos:5;pos:1" href="https://support.creditkarma.com/s/article/Intuit-Mint-and-Credit-Karma">在支持页面上特别指出</a>，“Credit Karma 的新体验不提供设置每月和类别预算的功能”，而是帮助用户“建立对其支出的认识”。然而，Mint 的净值功能最近被移植到 Credit Karma。</p><p> Mint 用户将能够通过从 Mint 应用程序登录 Credit Karma 来转移其帐户，之后他们将无法访问其 Mint 个人资料。如果他们不想切换，他们还可以下载或删除任何 Mint 数据。</p><p> <a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://www.reddit.com/r/mintuit/comments/17emsfy/merging_mint_with_credit_karma_experiences/">Reddit</a>上的一些 Mint 用户似乎对这一转变并不满意，其中一位用户表示，如果没有预算功能，“Mint 只是一个美化的支票簿寄存器。”与此同时，Intuit <a data-i13n="cpos:7;pos:1" href="https://www.engadget.com/intuit-owes-consumers-141-million-after-it-cheated-them-out-of-free-tax-services-090115518.html">最近因欺骗数百万低收入美国人支付本应免费的税务服务而被责令</a>支付 1.41 亿美元。</p><p><strong>更新，美国东部时间 2023 年 12 月 7 日下午 3:20：</strong>本文已更新，包含 Intuit 发言人的声明，该发言人向 Engadget 确认 Mint 将在 2024 年 3 月 24 日之前可用。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/intuit-is-looking-down-mint-its-popular-free-budget-tracking-app-054145229.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/intuit-is-closing-down-mint-its-popular-free-budget-tracking-app-054145229.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 9838fbfe-d102-4ed1-a35e-7f346c7fc6fc</guid><dc:creator>史蒂夫·登特</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Fri, 03 Nov 2023 05:41:45 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701980510</ingested><modified> 2023-12-07T20:21:54+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Finance]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Steve Dent]]></category><media:content height="888" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2Ffe3809c0-7a03-11ee-9ff7-ee057e5a3efd&amp;resize=1400%2C888&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=d553c0770a07acbec69dadc08ff170bd652498bc" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="888" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-11%2Ffe3809c0-7a03-11ee-9ff7-ee057e5a3efd&amp;resize=1400%2C888&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=99ec70ac6da6b99d5005338b97ff12395461bcdd" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Intuit/Mint]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Intuit is closing down its popular free budget-tracking app Mint]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Intuit is closing down its popular free budget-tracking app Mint]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Here's how to move your subscriptions off Google Podcasts before it shuts down]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p>今年早些时候，谷歌宣布将于 2024 年<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/google-podcasts-which-is-an-actual-thing-to-shut-down-next-year-172640308.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/google-podcasts-which-is-an-actual-thing-to-shut-down-next-year-172640308.html"><ins>关闭其独立播客应用程序</ins></a>。此后，该公司开始将播客转移到 YouTube 及其配套应用程序 YouTube Music 中。作为缓解过渡的一种方式，谷歌将为其当前的播客应用程序用户推出<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://blog.youtube/news-and-events/migrating-your-podcasts/" data-original-link="https://blog.youtube/news-and-events/migrating-your-podcasts/"><ins>迁移工具</ins></a>。借助该工具，美国用户将能够将他们最喜爱的播客订阅从 Google 播客转移到 YouTube Music，或将其导出以在其他播客应用中使用。</p><p>在接下来的几周内，迁移工具将通过 Google 播客中的横幅提供。 <a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://support.google.com/youtubemusic/answer/14151168" data-original-link="https://support.google.com/youtubemusic/answer/14151168"><ins>Google 帮助中心</ins></a>提供了有关如何使用迁移工具的分步说明。整个过程只需四个步骤，您需要在设备上安装 Google 播客和 YouTube Music 才能完成传输。传输后，Google 指出，所有内容可能需要几分钟才能显示在您的 YouTube 音乐库中。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>谷歌放弃其独立播客应用程序的举动并不完全令人意外。 Google Podcasts 自 2018 年以来一直存在，但它从未像 Overcast 和 Spotify 等类似应用程序那样迅速发展。 YouTube 已经成为<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-music-adds-podcasts-in-the-us-203332932.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-music-adds-podcasts-in-the-us-203332932.html"><ins>播客粉丝的热门目的地</ins></a>，最近的一项研究表明，超过<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://variety.com/2023/digital/news/google-podcasts-shutting-down-youtube-1235735517/" data-original-link="https://variety.com/2023/digital/news/google-podcasts-shutting-down-youtube-1235735517/"><ins>23%</ins></a>的播客听众将 YouTube 作为主要播放器。当今许多热门播客已可在 YouTube 上观看。对于平台上不可用的播客，用户可以通过 RSS feed 将节目直接添加到他们的 YouTube 音乐库中。这并不是谷歌的第一次牛仔竞技表演。早在 2020 年，该公司就取消了其独立音乐应用程序<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:6;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-music-google-play-music-library-transfer-150022835.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/youtube-music-google-play-music-library-transfer-150022835.html"><ins>Google Play Music</ins></a> ，转而使用 YouTube Music，并且还提供了一个将库转移到新应用程序的综合工具。</p><p> Google 播客将在 2024 年 3 月之前继续提供收听服务，之后用户将能够在 2024 年 7 月之前迁移或导出其订阅。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/heres-how-to-move-your-subscriptions-off-google-podcasts-before-it-shuts-down-194039938.html?src=rss ]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/heres-how-to-move-your-subscriptions-off-google-podcasts-before-it-shuts-down-194039938.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> 766911ac-e38d-48e1-874e-d067897c5f79</guid><dc:creator>斯蒂芬妮·巴恩斯</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 19:40:39 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701977156</ingested><modified> 2023-12-07T19:26:00+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[Information Technology]]></category><category><![CDATA[Software]]></category><category><![CDATA[Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[Mobile Apps]]></category><category><![CDATA[Technology & Electronics]]></category><category><![CDATA[Social & Online Media]]></category><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Stephanie Barnes]]></category><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fcc04aac0-9534-11ee-9bff-897fb8b3ea78&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=ae4d67cc7b9c98deb85eadf2af8f722777527d26" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="787" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fcc04aac0-9534-11ee-9bff-897fb8b3ea78&amp;resize=1400%2C787&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=24a1941cc334adc229c98602dc91f898f75a49ba" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Google]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Google Podcasts.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Google Podcasts]]></media:title></media:content></item><item><title><![CDATA[Meta's Threads is getting searchable topics (just don't call them hashtags)]]></title><description type="html"><![CDATA[<p> Meta 对 Threads 的最新更新将解决该公司 Twitter 竞争对手长期存在的功能请求：主题标签。该公司正在添加可搜索标签，以便人们更容易找到他们感兴趣的对话。</p><p>据该公司称，马克扎克伯格<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:1;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.threads.net/@zuck/post/Czrr520PZfh" data-original-link="https://www.threads.net/@zuck/post/Czrr520PZfh"><ins>上个月</ins></a>预览了这一变化，但该功能现在可供所有 Threads 用户使用。通过更新，Threads 用户可以为每篇帖子添加一个标签，并且该应用程序将显示标签建议和有关过去有多少其他用户使用过该主题的统计信息。</p><span id="end-legacy-contents"></span><p>值得注意的是，尽管可以在熟悉的 # 符号下找到该功能，但线程的标签与主题标签有点不同。正如 Instagram 负责人 Adam Mosseri 在<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:2;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/C0j7sSWvXTF" data-original-link="https://www.threads.net/@mosseri/post/C0j7sSWvXTF"><ins>一篇文章</ins></a>中指出的那样，线程标签可以包含空格和特殊字符。主题帖子也仅限于每个帖子一个标签，因此用户可能需要仔细考虑他们选择的标签。</p><p>标签一直是 Meta 的 Twitter 竞争对手长期以来要求的功能，许多用户质疑为什么该公司没有继承该功能，该功能在 Instagram 上也广泛使用。然而，Meta 似乎在采用该功能方面进展缓慢，因为担心它可能会在快速增长的平台上被滥用。</p><p>标签虽然在 Instagram 和 X 上长期流行，但也被滥用。在 Instagram 上，主题标签被用来传播<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:3;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-anti-vaxxers-coronavirus-conspiracy-theories-173021562.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/instagram-anti-vaxxers-coronavirus-conspiracy-theories-173021562.html"><ins>错误信息</ins></a>和其他<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:4;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/metas-apps-are-still-promoting-child-predation-content-report-finds-195357362.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/metas-apps-are-still-promoting-child-predation-content-report-finds-195357362.html"><ins>极其有问题的</ins></a>内容。虽然 Meta 已经对 Threads 上的<a data-i13n="elm:context_link;elmt:doNotAffiliate;cpos:5;pos:1" class="no-affiliate-link" href="https://www.engadget.com/meta-is-blocking-potentially-sensitive-topics-from-threads-search-231028963.html" data-original-link="https://www.engadget.com/meta-is-blocking-potentially-sensitive-topics-from-threads-search-231028963.html"><ins>“潜在敏感”</ins></a>内容施加了搜索限制，但对标签的额外限制可能会阻止其他类型的滥用。 “希望这种设计更多地关注社区标签，而不是参与黑客攻击，”莫塞里解释道。</p><p>但即使有这些限制，添加标签也有助于使 Threads 在跟踪实时对话方面更加有用。事实上，标签包含有关其使用量的统计数据，这表明它也可能是某种趋势主题功能的先驱，而这也是<a data-i13n="cpos:6;pos:1" href="https://techcrunch.com/2023/10/09/instagram-threads-preps-a-trending-topics-feature-in-battle-with-x/"><ins>许多猜测</ins></a>的根源。</p>本文最初发表在 Engadget 上：https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-is-getting-searchable-topics-just-dont-call-them-hashtags-191915209.html?src=rss]]>; </description><link/><![CDATA[https://www.engadget.com/metas-threads-is-getting-searchable-topics-just-dont-call-them-hashtags-191915209.html?src=rss]]><source_id> engadget_479</source_id><guid ispermalink="false"> fdad31cc-1673-4c3f-bd9d-19b8721ac1d1</guid><dc:creator>卡丽莎·贝尔</dc:creator><source/><![CDATA[Engadget]]><dc:publisher>恩杰特</dc:publisher><dc:rightsholder>恩杰特</dc:rightsholder><pubDate>Thu, 07 Dec 2023 19:19:15 +0000</pubDate><ingested> 1701976755</ingested><modified> 2023-12-07T19:19:20+00:00 </modified><category><![CDATA[site|engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[provider_name|Engadget]]></category><category><![CDATA[region|US]]></category><category><![CDATA[language|en-US]]></category><category><![CDATA[author_name|Karissa Bell]]></category><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fb22fc260-952f-11ee-beba-7dd1b99b88a9&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=57b147c8cb9b6c8cfee1665330991443da5fcc8f" width="1400"><media:keywords>标题</media:keywords><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[1]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[ ]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[ ]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[ ]]></media:title></media:content><media:content height="933" medium="image" url="https://o.aolcdn.com/images/dims?image_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2023-12%2Fb22fc260-952f-11ee-beba-7dd1b99b88a9&amp;resize=1400%2C933&amp;client=19f2b5e49a271b2bde77&amp;signature=b6382c279ba4443c12f1b070a112169b1ead135a" width="1400"><media:media_html><![CDATA[ ]]></media:media_html><dc:identifier><![CDATA[2]]></dc:identifier><media:credit><![CDATA[Meta]]></media:credit><media:description><![CDATA[Meta's Threads app with its new tagging feature.]]></media:description><media:title><![CDATA[Threads tags topics]]></media:title></media:content></item></channel></rss>